fields.name: Whitening Strips
fields.description: Experience the power of natural ingredients with our organic teeth whitening strips. Made for a brighter smile, these easy-to-use strips are effective and offer visible results within a week. Each pack contains 20 strips, all carefully formulated with organic, fluoride-free ingredients that work gently on your teeth. Enjoy a healthy, radiant smile without compromising on the health of your mouth. Ingredients: Carbamide peroxide, Glycerin, Carbomer, Peppermint oil, Potassium nitrate

fields.name: Whitening Toothpaste
fields.description: Unleash the strength of nature with our powerful whitening toothpaste. Designed to eliminate stains and enhance the brightness of your teeth, this toothpaste is crafted from organic, fluoride-free ingredients. It ensures the robust health of your teeth and maintains fresh breath. It's also available in a variety of natural flavors for a unique brushing experience. Ingredients Carbamide peroxide, Glycerin, Carbomer, Peppermint oil, Potassium nitrate

fields.name: Whitening Kit
fields.description: Experience professional-level teeth whitening at the comfort of your home with our complete teeth whitening kit. This kit is meticulously assembled with an organic, cruelty-free whitening gel, trays, LED light, and comprehensive instructions. It ensures safe and effective results, helping you achieve a dazzling smile naturally. Ingredients Carbamide peroxide, Glycerin, Carbomer, Peppermint oil, Potassium nitrate

fields.name: Whitening Gel
fields.description: Discover the potential of our high-quality teeth whitening gel designed for use with custom trays. Its professional-strength formula, enriched with organic, cruelty-free, and fluoride-free ingredients, ensures optimal results while being safe for your enamel. Experience a significant difference in the brightness of your smile without compromising on safety. Ingredients Carbamide peroxide, Glycerin, Carbomer, Peppermint oil, Potassium nitrate

fields.name: Whitening Pen
fields.description: Introducing our handy teeth whitening pen, your perfect companion for on-the-go use. Formulated with organic, cruelty-free, and fluoride-free ingredients, it offers an easy application process for touch-ups, ensuring your smile stays bright wherever you go. Its compact, travel-friendly design means a confident smile is always within reach. Ingredients Carbamide peroxide, Glycerin, Carbomer, Peppermint oil, Potassium nitrate
